===簽證===
:參見：[[塞爾維亞簽證政策|塞爾維亞簽證政策]]和[[塞爾維亞公民簽證要求|塞爾維亞公民簽證要求]]
:以及：[[越南簽證政策|越南簽證政策]]和[[越南公民簽證要求|越南公民簽證要求]]
兩國公民皆須申請簽證方可入境對方國家。持有[[塞爾維亞護照|塞爾維亞護照]]的[[塞爾維亞人口|塞爾維亞公民]]可以申請電子簽證入境越南，停留不超過30天。若前往[[富国岛|富国岛]]，可在岛上免签证停留30天。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://discoverphuquoc.com/customsvisas.html#a4 |title=Phu Quoc Specific Decisions |accessdate=2020-08-24 |archive-date=2014-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223162312/http://discoverphuquoc.com/customsvisas.html#a4 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.vietseatourist.vn/News/category1/news-57/No-visa-required-for-tourists-to-Phu-Quoc-on-short-stay.html |title=No visa required for tourists to Phu Quoc on short stay |access-date=2014-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701095940/http://www.vietseatourist.vn/News/category1/news-57/No-visa-required-for-tourists-to-Phu-Quoc-on-short-stay.html |archive-date=2017-07-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.phuquocislandguide.com/phu-quoc-visa/#2015-vietnam-visa-updates|title=Phu Quoc visa policy|accessdate=|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2017-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171223042509/https://www.phuquocislandguide.com/phu-quoc-visa/#2015-vietnam-visa-updates|dead-url=no}}</ref>

持有[[越南護照|越南護照]]的[[越南人口|越南公民]]必須提前申請簽證方可入境塞爾維亞，如果在停留期間持有有效的[[欧洲联盟|欧盟]]、[[申根区|申根地区]]各成员国或[[美国|美国]]签证，則可以在180天内免簽停留90天。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.lisbon.mfa.gov.rs/newstext.php?subaction=showfull&id=1415622267&ucat=19&template=Frontpage3&|title=Embassy of the Republic of Serbia in the Portuguese Republic|accessdate=20 January 2015|publisher=Lisbon.mfa.gov.rs|archive-date=2019-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190814123037/http://www.lisbon.mfa.gov.rs/newstext.php?subaction=showfull&id=1415622267&ucat=19&template=Frontpage3&|dead-url=no}}</ref>

南斯拉夫於2000年與越南簽署互免外交和公務護照持有人簽證的協定。該協定由塞爾維亞繼承，因此，外交和公務護照持有人可以免簽證入境對方國家。<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://www.mofa.gov.vn/vi/cn_vakv/euro/nr060911172945/ns170706161025 | title=THÔNG TIN CƠ BẢN VỀ CỘNG HÒA XÉC-BI-A | publisher=越南外交部 |date=2018-07-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mfa.gov.rs/en/consular-affairs/entry-serbia/visa-regime|title=Consular countries|accessdate=20 January 2015|publisher=Mfa.gov.rs|archive-date=2017-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170727215610/http://www.mfa.gov.rs/en/consular-affairs/entry-serbia/visa-regime|dead-url=no}}</ref>

